  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li>The character has logic to demonstrate how the component works.</li><li>There is also the logic of combo attacks (2 attacks with hands and 2 attacks with legs) and dodges.</li><li>Logic apply damage with hit reaction.</li><li>Game Mod also has logic to demonstrate how the component works in different modes</li><li>Animation only demonstrations.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Number of Blueprints</strong>: 3</p><p><strong>Number of Components</strong>: 1</p><p><strong>Animations</strong>: default for demo</p><p><strong>Input</strong>: None required, though demo uses keyboard, mouse and gamepad inputs.</p><p><strong>Network Replicated</strong>: (Yes)</p><p><strong>Supported Development Platforms</strong>: (Windows, Mac)</p><p><strong>Supported Target Build Platforms</strong>: (Windows, Mac)</p><p><strong>Documentation:Â </strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_l70usyjKJToGloZgGcWJH7L6kb7DaR8mxS8OzY2c_Y/edit?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Link to document</strong></a></p><p><strong>If you need use for mobile or gamepad: Turn on Touch interface or add input events</strong></p>",
